Posts.Content:
Do you take contraceptive? Some time they may be a cause. I am not a doctor but a happily married man. My wife started the contraceptive is but we decided to take her off because of the side effects. You may want to do some research. Doctors usually don't take seriously any side effects of any medicine. 
I hope you feel better and nothing is serious.
Good luck and best wishes.
